with_transcript.title: The Biggest AI News in History Just Dropped
with_transcript.description:
The biggest AI news in history just dropped. OpenAI has announced Q* (Q-Star), a breakthrough in AI reasoning capabilities that has caused chaos at OpenAI, with researchers sending letters to the board about the dangers of this technology. Let's explore what Q* is, why it's so significant, and what this means for the future of AI.

Join AI Insiders: https://www.patreon.com/AIExplained
